{"tid":1810663,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Digitimes:iPhone SE2 3月冇 或年底甚至2021先有","createTime":"2020-01-04T05:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T10:26:15.000Z","uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"46587f19f0269068e7cacd11a255ad11d86e42ed","tid":1810663,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>傳六款 iPhone 今年發表   當中兩款使用 LCD 屏幕</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/0104-3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F0104-3a.jpg&h=b822d7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣科技業界新聞網站《DigiTimes》日前引述供應鏈消息指，Apple 將會在 2020 年推出多達 6 款全新的 iPhone，該名消息人士表示曾經收到 Apple 的產品路線圖。比起 2019 年只有 iPhone 11、iPhone 11 Pro 和 Pro Max，今年的機款多一倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《DigiTimes》指 6 款新 iPhone 當中，有 4 款將會採用 OLED 屏幕，而另外兩款則採用 LCD 屏幕。使用 LCD 屏幕的可能是價格相對較低的 iPhone SE 2，消息指將會有 5.5 吋和 6.1 吋屏幕兩個版本。報導提到負責為 Apple 生產 A14 Bionic 處理器的台積電，同時會為新 iPhone 提供採用 INFO_AIP 技術的天線模組。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">期待 iPhone SE 2 會在今年年初發表的消費者，可能會失望而回，因為《DigiTimes》的消息指 Apple 打算到今年年底，甚至 2021 年年初才會將兩款 iPhone SE 2 推出市場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/04/six-new-iphone-for-2020/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F04%2Fsix-new-iphone-for-2020%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=03c04daa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/04/six-new-iphone-for-2020/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你叫我地班SE撚點算等4年都未換到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3220dd6598e1ace5b1a1215d04b29c452266fb7a","tid":1810663,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a48be63a640d987789deda2c8d8a0b6baac37b5","tid